reviewText: We brought this Wii Game for our daughter and she loves it.  I highly recommend this game.  Lots of fun for child and parents.

Standing Ovation Dance Party is a great video for children to watch to get a work out and a good dance.  It accompanies the movie STANDING OVATION. Need your kids to burn off some energy?  Have them participate watching this video.  Enjoy and DANCE!

I really don't like these messages for our kids. Dancing and singing should be for fun and for the purpose of education not for the sake of performance. Sending out the wrong messages to kids can really hurt in the long run, with all sorts of delusions of grandeur. Its' really not what we should be aiming at.
